headline.main: No. 6 Oregon Downs Oregon State 80-59, Wins Share of Pac-12
headline.print_headline: No. 6 Oregon Downs Oregon State 80-59, Wins Share of Pac-12

lead_paragraph: Oregon coach Dana Altman figures it could be decades before his players truly appreciate what it means to win consecutive Pac-12 championships.
